    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior upholstery exhibits some staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will eventually need attention for a minor oil leak and aging suspension components. It's a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic and mechanical character.",
      "price": 20000.0,
