    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for anyone needing a dependable daily driver. The exterior does show its age with some noticeable scratches on the doors and a few minor dings, and the interior has some visible wear on the upholstery. However, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, making it a functional and honest option for the price.",
